This can lead to problems and confusion down the road when mixing other JS libraries or trying to embed multiple p5 sketches on the same page. So it is better to use &quot;instance mode&quot;. 

Here is example using `@NpmPackage` in Vaadin:

     @Route(&quot;/p5demo&quot;)
